@node NAMEL "Nameless Race"

@{b}Nameless Race@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = DK(U1)
Type    = Summon Nameless Race (*/*)
Cost    = 3B
Artist  = Quinton Hoover

Text(DK): Trample
          Pay * life when bringing Nameless Race into play. Effects that
          prevent or redirect damage may not be used to counter this loss
          of life. When Nameless Race is brought into play, * may not be
          greater than the total number of white cards all opponents have
          in play and in their graveyards.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_N.guide/NAMEL}

